d! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cge1665702892418.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cge1665702892418.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cge1665702892418.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cge1665702892418\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Get Information About DDE Supported System Topics\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">To obtain information on current system topics, run a <code class=\"ph codeph\">uDDErequest</code>\n      with the data listed. Set the topic string to <code class=\"ph codeph\">System</code> and the item string to\n      one of the following values:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"cge1665702892418__table_d3551e1_d3552e1_d3553e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Supported system topics</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cge1665702892418__table_d3551e1_d3552e1_d3553e1__entry__1\">\n Item\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cge1665702892418__table_d3551e1_d3552e1_d3553e1__entry__2\">\n Returns\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cge1665702892418__table_d3551e1_d3552e1_d3553e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Topics</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cge1665702892418__table_d3551e1_d3552e1_d3553e1__entry__2\">\n All currently present form components.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cge1665702892418__table_d3551e1_d3552e1_d3553e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Formats</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cge1665702892418__table_d3551e1_d3552e1_d3553e1__entry__2\">All supported data formats. Currently, only\n                        <code class=\"ph codeph\">CF_TEXT</code> is supported. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cge1665702892418__table_d3551e1_d3552e1_d3553e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Status</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cge1665702892418__table_d3551e1_d3552e1_d3553e1__entry__2\">Status of Uniface DDE server. This is either\n                        <code class=\"ph codeph\">Ready</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">Busy</code>. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cge1665702892418__table_d3551e1_d3552e1_d3553e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">SysItems</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cge1665702892418__table_d3551e1_d3552e1_d3553e1__entry__2\">\n All currently supported system items.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"cge1665702892418__note_w5805ab1b5b3_w5806ab1b5_w5807ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> All information is returned in a tab-separated list.</div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wgz1719591021043.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>DDE Syntax Rules</a></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gkm1665702892640.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" cl